\r\n; ******* Voxel Debris types *******\r\n
; Translucent = is the debris to be drawn with translucency (def=no)?\r\n
; Elasticity = \"bounciness\" of the object [should be 0.0 through 1.0] (def=0.75)\r\n
; MinAngularVelocity = minimum rate at which the debris is to spin in degrees (def=0.0)\r\n
; MaxAngularVelocity = maximum rate at which the debris is to spin in degrees (def=10.0)\r\n
; Duration = max number of frames to let the debris exist (def=30)\r\n
; MinZVel = minimum starting Z velocity (def=3.5)\r\n
; MaxZVel = maximum starting Z velocity (def=5.0)\r\n
; MaxXYVel = maximim starting lateral velocity (def=15.0)\r\n
; ShareBodyData = Get the voxel data from another Type\'s body voxel data (def = no)?\r\n
; ShareTurretData = Get the voxel data from another Type\'s turret voxel data (def = no)?\r\n
; ShareBarrelData = Get the VOXEL data from another Type\'s barrel voxel data (def = no)?\r\n
; ShareSource = name of the object to share voxel data from (def = none)\r\n
; VoxelIndex = voxel piece within the voxel data to use (def = 0)\r\n
; StartSound = sound to play when the voxel anim is created (def = VOC_NONE).\r\n
; BounceSound = sound to play when the voxel anim bounces (def = VOC_NONE).\r\n
; ExpireSound = sound to play when the voxel anim expires (def = VOC_NONE).\r\n
; BounceAnim = animation to launch when the voxel anim bounces (def = ANIM_NONE).\r\n
; ExpireAnim = animation to launch when the voxel anim expires (def = ANIM_NONE).\r\n
; TrailerAnim = animation to trail behind the object (usually smoke or flame)\r\n
; DamageRadius = the debris damages objects that it hits if they\'re closer than this distance\r\n
; Damage = amount of damage to apply to objects that are hit\r\n
; Warhead = warhead to use for damage purposes\r\n
; AttachedSystem = particle system to attach to the voxel anim\r\n
; Spawns = the particle spawned when this voxel debris explodes (def = none)\r\n
; SpawnCount = number of particles spawned [on average] (def = 0)\r\n

